few inconsequential Twitter fights, and moved on.

Not long after, I realized where the disconnect was. I went back to the=
 same=20
experts and explained: in the wild, in really dangerous situations=E2=80=
=8A=E2=80=94=E2=80=8Aeven when=20
people are being hunted by men with guns=E2=80=8A=E2=80=94=E2=80=8Awhen=
 encryption and security fails,=20
no one stops talking. They just hope they don=E2=80=99t get caught.

